<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="theirs-pron">theirs <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðeəz/    美 /ðerz/  </p>
<p>[名词性物主代词，用作主语、宾语、表语等]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>他们的；她们的；它们的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She managed to hold on to her job when several of her colleagues lost theirs.
她的几位同事都失业了，而她却设法保住了自己的职位。</p></div></div>